## ğŸ”§ Development

### Frontend Development
```bash
cd streamlit_funplayer/frontend
npm install
npm start  # Runs on localhost:3001
```

### Testing with Streamlit
```bash
# In project root
streamlit run funplayer.py
```

### Building for Production
```bash
cd frontend  
npm run build
pip install -e .  # Install with built frontend
```

